===Noun===
{{wikipediapar|Red Brick universities}}
'''[[red]] [[brick]] [[university]]'''
#{{British}} any [[traditional]] [[British]] university other than [[Oxford]] or [[Cambridge]], especially one founded in the [[Victorian]] age in a large city

